## CODE STANDARDS

### Component Props
- Use TypeScript interfaces
- Make `viewMode` required where needed
- Provide sensible defaults

### Tailwind Classes
- Use design system colors (slate, blue, red, indigo)
- Avoid arbitrary values unless necessary
- Mobile-first: base styles for mobile, `md:` for desktop

### File Naming
- Components: PascalCase (`Term.tsx`)
- Utilities: camelCase (`formatDate.ts`)
- Articles: kebab-case (`stroke-basics.tsx`)

